replies.body:
Rezonate - Canvas

Thought:
I really think this song gets people up and moving stronger than every from being KO'd by a bully or whatever... And i really hope people listen to it more often to understand the actual meaning of the song, the message. If thy want to hear the truth contact me on this thread, but honestly listen to this song MULTIPLE times and hopefully you understand it.
Life always has a meaning, whether rich or famous, Poor or Shy, whatever it is you have something that NOBODY has, you. You are your own person, if you had a hard experience, you have to understand that fighting for what you want, is the way to get through. Hit the bully of the cliff with, the force you remake in your mind, take them to a place where they never were, make them think more. Destroy their bad side, Destroy opposing challenges, whether its a test or even more extreme. You might have friends... but you can't always rely on backup from them. However if you gain the power that you deserve, need, and want, you will do ANYTHING, but patients is key. If you are fighting, going against the other, remember that you have to wait till they break down.. Until then, get destroying their defense, their guard. And NEVER let the challenge get the best of you!
                             ~Max 2014
